OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,FBusinesses on a street in South London
OL,7,Fsay they're worried for the future as
OL,8,Fthe council raises rent by more than
OL,9,F100 per cent.
OL,11,FThe shops on Crossthwaite Avenue in
OL,12,Fthe London Borough of Southwark,
OL,13,Finclude a supermarket, hairdresses,
OL,14,Fpharmacy, laundrette and post office.
OL,16,FCustomers have described the parade as
OL,17,Fa "a local community hub".
OL,19,FNasrin Jahanshiri opened Crystal
OL,20,FLaunderette in 2012 with her late
OL,21,Fhusband.
