OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,F"It's hard work but the community are
OL,7,Fvery nice and very customers,
OL,8,Funderstanding - I feel like I am part
OL,9,Fof the family," she said.
OL,11,F"They invite me to their homes, we
OL,12,Fspend time together, being in this
OL,13,Fenvironment makes it easier for me to
OL,14,Fwork seven days a week...it's not just
OL,15,Fa job, the community is like my
OL,16,Ffamily, they look after me."
OL,18,FMs Jahanshiri's businesses is one of
OL,19,Ffive that has been given the increase
OL,20,F- something that she says she "cannot
OL,21,Fcover".
