OL,6,FMs Jahanshiri's husband died six years
OL,7,Fago, and she has spent that time
OL,8,Fpaying off loans and continuing to
OL,9,Fbuild the business.
OL,11,FThe pandemic also put a lot of
OL,12,Fpressure on small businesses like
OL,13,Fhers, and this news has caused further
OL,14,F"anxiety, stress and frustration".
OL,16,F"This business was really an
OL,17,Fachievement for my husband, and all my
OL,18,Fmemories are here. I feel like I
OL,19,F(will) lose him again," she said.
