OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,FAnjih Supermarket is another family
OL,7,Fbusiness concerned about the increases.
OL,9,FIt has been in the area for 15 years
OL,10,Fand even opens on Christmas Day.
OL,12,FAnijan Nirmal's family own the shop.
OL,13,FHe said: "If you increase the rent,
OL,14,Fthat cost has to be paid by us, all
OL,15,Fthat increase has to go somewhere it
OL,16,Fwill go into the price of the goods.
OL,18,F"The stuff we sell that is price
OL,19,Flocked, we can't do that anymore so
OL,20,Fwe're going to have to sell it for
OL,21,Fhigher.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
