OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,F"One of the major things of having a
OL,7,Fbusiness in this area is to serve the
OL,8,Flocal community, and one of the things
OL,9,FI looked at was all the surrounding
OL,10,Fflats and houses," she explains.
OL,12,F"I've had a rent increase, it was more
OL,13,Fthan what I could afford initially but
OL,14,Fwe were able to negotiate a price but
OL,15,FI certainly can't afford the new price.
OL,17,F"I was flabbergasted, and the thing
OL,18,Fabout it was there wasn't an option,
OL,19,Fthey were saying it is renewable
OL,20,Fhowever there's no option - yes or no
OL,21,Fyou need to agree. It was criminal.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
