OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,F"Everyone will be happy we have a
OL,7,Fsustainable, affordable rent that's
OL,8,Fwhat we need to stay here. Otherwise
OL,9,Fmost certainly wont be able to
OL,10,Fmaintain that sort of increase."
OL,12,FA petition has been started by
OL,13,Fresident, Jenifer Milner, and is
OL,14,Fcalling on Southwark Council to "re-
OL,15,Fthink their extortionate rent
OL,16,Fincreases".
