OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,F"We all use these shops because
OL,7,Fthey're within walking distance and
OL,8,Fthey're essential services and they've
OL,9,Fbeen here a very long time," said Ms
OL,10,FMilner.
OL,12,F"It's good to come here because they
OL,13,Fknow us and they're very quick, if the
OL,14,Fcustomer doesn't turn up - Bim (from
OL,15,Fthe Post Office) will send out and
OL,16,Fcheck if the customer is okay. It's a
OL,17,Freal neighborhood community hub that
OL,18,Fwe really value."
