OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,FIn response, Cllr John Batteson,
OL,7,Fcabinet member for climate emergency,
OL,8,Fjobs, and business, said:
OL,10,F"We very much champion smaller local
OL,11,Fbusinesses. These issues stem directly
OL,12,Ffrom the pandemic years when we paused
OL,13,Frent reviews and lease renewals as
OL,14,Fpart of our business support efforts.
OL,15,FThose delays in renewals have left the
OL,16,Fleases far out of step with the
OL,17,Fcurrent market rates for the
OL,18,Fproperties in question.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
