OL,3,CShopkeepers appeal to council after
OL,4,Crents are raised by over 100%
OL,6,F"We have been working with the
OL,7,Fbusiness owners on Crossthwaite Avenue
OL,8,Fto find a solution to the issues
OL,9,Fsurrounding lease renewals and have
OL,10,Fused this opportunity to engage with
OL,11,Fall businesses on the parade rather
OL,12,Fthan just the couple who were
OL,13,Fimmediately due for renewals.
OL,15,F"We know how much of an anchor these
OL,16,Fbusinesses are to the local community
OL,17,Fand we are committed to finding a
OL,18,Fresolution so they remain serving
OL,19,Flocal people. I'm confident we'll be
OL,20,Fable to do so in the coming weeks."
